description: The foodies on the streets of Northern Virginia and Washington DC are delighting in Ali Baba DC Kebab’s authentic and delicious Turkish cuisine. Only the best and freshest ingredients are used in their mouthwatering menu, which includes Doner Kebab, Lamb Chops, Falafel, and so much more. For a bite full of wonderful flavor, be sure to come out to Ali Baba DC Kebab!!
name: Ali Baba DC Kebab
